name: Wellhealthbook
body:
### Welcome to WellHealthBook.
WellHealthBook is an open source Electronic Medical Record (EMR) and Practice Management System (PMS) based on ClearHealth(TM) Technology.

```
$ git clone https://github.com/spydroid/WellHealthBook.git
```

### Authors and Contributors
In 2014, SpyDroid (@spydroid) starting forking ClearHealth as WellHealthBook.

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with WellHealthBook? Create a ticket using our issue tracker at https://github.com/spydroid/WellHealthBook/issues or contact support@wellhealthbook.org and weâ€™ll help you sort it out.
